column2: Dimension used for sorting border cards.

column17: 0 = Participant failed the pre-switch phase of the standard version.
column18: 1 = Participant passed the pre-switch phase of the standard version, but failed the post-switch phase.
column19: 2 = Participant passed the pre-switch and post-switch phases of the standard version, but failed the border version.
column20: 3 = Participant passed the pre-switch and post-switch phases of the standard version and passed the border version.
